title: the Breville  Boss To Go Personal Blender 30 sec TVC
description:
The Personal Blender that pulverises whole fruits and vegetables, nuts and leafy greens, up to 42% finer*.
With a smooth café tumbler with no uncomfortable clips or threads for a nicer drinking experience.

Smoother Smoothies from a smoother cup.
